Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见和希亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就翘一天课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 说的到简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被老师知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知会受到什么惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛讨厌和我约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩的话可以改日…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是用这种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你最近根本就不陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 要跟我约会一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看着我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会放你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么求你都不答应的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人把我的裙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下肯定迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你就那么喜欢去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 这是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天有重要的话想对凛说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校没办法说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就不能理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫 我太太怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很难说出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夫人只剩下一周的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在看电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的话到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只能是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 好可怕～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,320)\fs-1}（赶快好起来吧…）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,320)\fs-1}（没关系的）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骼膊好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过来还真少见 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛早上说要去亚沙前辈那里 先走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没到学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直等着他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果被他放鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是… 遇上什么事故了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是被诱拐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱拐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次连芙蓉也不见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈 希望不要生气…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这件怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不错… 有点不像希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么做真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这次就穿那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你不必那么害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和凛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的一切都给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希 希亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…你也玩够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了晚饭用的材料后就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要两个人待一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的是希亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是希亚的话那还有谁是希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 到那边坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真安静啊 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么坐着感觉好像世界上只有我们两个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是凛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上吃什么啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分 太过分了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为希亚总是没有什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有求你这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你希望一直那个样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直没有结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直维持着那种不温不火的关系比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直那样子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要怎么去面对凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛… 很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚你这么主动也不接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为希亚的话一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚的话一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成功然后获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚你不是喜欢凛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向凛传达心意的话 这不是最好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚你不想获得幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为… 不能只让我一个人获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算撒谎也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你的内心里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算希亚你这么说 我也一点都不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没办法获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的为我着想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚你就自己获得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那么说我还是时常会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希亚你要获得幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 土见 枫 小琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从枫那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见也终于被警察叫走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于是什么意思 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就料定你绝对会有这么一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有跟其他的人说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么是天罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比平常还重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扪胸自问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我倒是被枫吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真的会报警
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是亚沙前辈说了多余的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那之后我有多麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便放鸽子到底是谁的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 凛难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏枫替我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没受老师罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿能陪我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫秋高气爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是平时的希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但昨天的希亚也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内还有一个希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很突然你可能不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该有个一起出生的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹是谁也不希望被生下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我平安出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可悲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我接受了消失在母亲腹中的那孩子的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一个人消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我不可替代的唯一的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也永远在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我 两人一体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是平时在这里的希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 还有一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内有两颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 普通生活中的我是平时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的时候 欢笑的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时里面的我也会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一直孤单地在我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能光让表面的我获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就对不起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 多亏了凛 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她讨厌这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想着不能一个人获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她却不是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风风火火 心急火燎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给凛添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是是她的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直期盼着此刻的我能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她给了我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为莉希爱萨斯 有了获取幸福的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛肯定还有其他喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了要让凛更了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还瞒着你重要的事 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下心里终于舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要记住这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神界是一夫多妻制 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很喜欢凛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了凛大人 也为了为了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 SHUFFLE第18话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.34,0:24:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不行啊
